    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "That's a great start for the kids. Can you add a few specific examples of landmark Supreme Court cases where substantive due process was used to protect those liberties? I'd like them to see how it actually works in practice to defend people’s rights.",
      "source": "evaluator"
