    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Those are really powerful examples for the class. Since there's sometimes debate about whether these rulings are actually strictly following the Constitution or if they are just \"judicial activism,\" how should I explain to my students the idea that substantive due process is the primary way we ensure the government can't violate fundamental rights that aren't explicitly written in the text?",
